<%= yield %>

---

Reply with entry for date: <%= Time.now.in_time_zone(@user.time_zone).strftime("%Y-%m-%d") %>.

You can always send a new email to <%= "#{@user.email_key}@post.dayjot.com" %> to create a new entry.
The entry will be created for the current date, and any subsequent emails within the same day will be appended to that entry.